Class WMultiParser

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.utils.wysiwyg.WMultiParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
Multi
public class WMultiParser extends Object implements Multi
WYSIWYG-editor Multi Parser Parses a MULTI string. Generates a WMessage containing a list of one or more WPage objects each of which contain a list of WToken objects.
Author:
John L. Stanley - SRF Consulting
